,"tid":230710,"uid":943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"我都諗唔明，咁樣好難篤啊"},{"pid":"52bb9b756db68c561b3b18b267a03e99ce8c53c2","tid":230710,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"手法問題，我做茶記個個師父手法不一"},{"pid":"c7234cdc106bff88b0d56dbdbbbb0d5e7a148624","tid":230710,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:56:26.000Z","msg":"落檸檬先啲茶會濁"},{"pid":"c31a1413b5f68a295ae47d15bffa399629a672bd","tid":230710,"uid":52503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係諗唔明，點解唔可以掉返轉檸檬放底先加冰，次次篤親檸檬都要將 d 檸檬隊落底但又比 d 冰阻住哂，有時仲會篤到連冰都飛到成枱都係。</blockquote><br />\n小甜就係檸檬係面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n方便樓面分邊杯係小甜邊杯唔係"},{"pid":"52b10debaba99f83af9668849317e5591a379254","tid":230710,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:00:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落檸檬先啲茶會濁</blockquote><br />\n但濁之餘會唔會影響茶味？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實唔剩止檸茶，有檸檬既凍飲都有呢個問題。"},{"pid":"22d46ee67ba2156d00582e152567ca60c53235bb","tid":230710,"uid":27946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"識沖既水吧凍檸茶 一定係 檸檬係底 大量冰 糖水 茶 咁沖 <br />\n<br />\n但都有d想整得靚就會檸檬薄d放面"},{"pid":"ea578c45a5ca8667f7feb696a3f7926fcfabe5e7","tid":230710,"uid":5218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"有時用隻長羹篤檸檬經常都會比冰阻住而插到落底，一插落底隻羹就會比檸檬戟住，要用埋枝飲筒解圍，搞到好論盡，有時剩係用飲筒篤，篤篤下篤左落舊冰度搞到連枝飲筒中間都爆開埋飲到中間啜唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62808d55799cd9acc597ed0ac987b47d8b78aea","tid":230710,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T04:14:48.000Z","msg":"有無做水吧嘅解釋下"},{"pid"